ability.name: ability
ability.description: Grants or revokes a player ability.

advancement.name: advancement
advancement.description: Gives, removes, or checks player advancements.

clone.name: clone
clone.description: Copies blocks from one place to another.

data.name: data
data.description: Gets, merges, and removes block entity and entity NBT data.

debug.name: debug
debug.description: Starts or stops a debugging session.

deop.name: deop
deop.description: Revokes operator status from a player.

fill.name: fill
fill.description: Fills a region with a specific block.

forceload.name: forceload
forceload.description: Forces chunks to constantly be loaded or not.

gamerule.name: gamerule
gamerule.description: Sets or queries a game rule value.

give.name: give
give.description: Gives an item to a player.

kick.name: kick
kick.description: Kicks a player off a server.

loot.name: loot
loot.description: Drops items from an inventory slot onto the ground.

msg.name: msg
msg.description: Displays a private message to other players.

op.name: op
op.description: Grants operator status to a player.

publish.name: publish
publish.description: Opens single-player world to local network.

reload.name: reload
reload.description: Reloads loot tables, advancements, and functions from disk.

say.name: say
say.description: Displays a message to multiple players.

schedule.name: schedule
schedule.description: Delays the execution of a function.

scoreboard.name: scoreboard
scoreboard.description: Manages objectives, players, teams, and tags.

setblock.name: setblock
setblock.description: Changes a block to another block.

setidletimeout.name: setidletimeout
setidletimeout.description: Sets the time before idle players are kicked.

setmaxplayers.name: setmaxplayers
setmaxplayers.description: Sets the maximum number of players allowed to join.

spawnpoint.name: spawnpoint
spawnpoint.description: Sets the spawn point for a player.

tell.name: tell
tell.description: Displays a private message to other players.

tellraw.name: tellraw
tellraw.description: Displays a JSON message to players.

testforblock.name: testforblock
testforblock.description: Tests whether a block is in a location.

testforblocks.name: testforblocks
testforblocks.description: Tests whether the blocks in two regions match.

tickingarea.name: tickingarea
tickingarea.description: Add, remove, or list ticking areas.

time.name: time
time.description: Changes or queries the world's game time.

trigger.name: trigger
trigger.description: Sets a trigger to be activated.

w.name: w
w.description: Displays a private message to other players.
